title: Case Was Received
body: On March 22, 2021, we received your Form I-751, Petition to Remove Conditions on Residence, Receipt Number YSC2190136000, and sent you the receipt notice that describes how we will process your case. Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you have any questions, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Case Rejected For Incorrect Fee And Form Not Signed
body: On April 12, 2021, we rejected your Form I-601A, Application for Provisional Unlawful Presence Waiver, Receipt Number YSC2190136017, because you did not sign the form and the fee you paid was incorrect. We mailed your case back to you, including any supporting materials and the payment. Please follow the instructions to resubmit your case. If you have any questions, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Case Was Rejected Because It Was Improperly Filed
body: On April 12, 2021, we rejected your Form I-601A, Application for Provisional Unlawful Presence Waiver, Receipt Number YSC2190136018, because it was not filed correctly. We mailed your case back to you, including any supporting materials and fee. Please follow the instructions to resubmit your case. If you have any questions, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
